<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
<aka>I want to live the way</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nå vil jeg prise
 Jesus i livet mitt her,
 nå vil jeg gi mitt alt
 til min Frelser så kjær.
 Nå vil jeg leve for Ham
 helt til solen går ned.
 Han har gitt meg
 en underfull fred.

[V2]
 I want to live the way
 He wants me to live,
 I want to give until there's just
 no more to give.
 I want to love, love till
 there's just no more love,
 for I can never ever
 outlove the Lord.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>Nå vil jeg prise Jesus</title>
</song>